title: Young Business Professionals ‘Superhero Dinner’ Honors Rosie Collin (Texas A&M University - Corpun Christi)
text: ( Source : Texas A&M University - Corpun Christi) CORPUS CHRISTI, Texas - The Young Business Professionals of the Coastal Bend (YBPCB) honored an accomplished member of the community at their fourth annual Superhero Dinner fundraising
